				<div class="news-suject">
					<a href="#">Q. What is the difference between Auto-Debit and Manual Deposit?<span class="faq-arrow"></span></a>
					<div class="news-toggle">
						<p class="news-text">
							Auto-Debit and Manual Deposit differs in their withdrawal schemes and authentication methods.<br/>
							For Auto-Debit, we do automatically subract the exact remittance amount from the customer's registered bank account. There's no need for the customer to manually transfer or deposit the money to our virtual account. (Some bank accounts such as 평생 계좌 cannot be regsitered under auto-debit service.)<br/>
							 [Manual] : When requesting a remittance, a virtual bank account number of HANPASS is issued. If you deposit the payment to that account number, the remittance will be processed.
						</p>
